### Whatâ€™s in the repo (ready right now)

- `README.md` â€” full docs, multi-agent tips, model mapping, staking, troubleshooting
- `setup.sh` â€” installs EverClaw proxy + guardian into `~/.everclaw`, starts it as service (launchd/systemd), safely patches `~/.tinyclaw/settings.json` + adds env vars
- `settings.patch.json` â€” exact snippet merged into your global + per-agent configs
